registerHarvestSubmission(string,string,.details: Register a Harvest submission - it should add the Harvest submission to the array of Harvest submissions i.e. harvestMap.

params._geolocation: Geographical location of where the produce is harvested e.g. -33.961059,18.4110411
params._harvestID: Unique ID for supplier-produce and harvest combination e.g. 1b26557b-20f3-4ea2-81d2-e54c5a9a40f7
params._harvestTimeStamp: Date and time at which produce is harvested e.g. 20190620 16:10:55
params._photoHash: Hash of photo BLOB stored in relational database e.g. abc01...
params._supplierproduceID: Unique ID (per supplier-produce combination) e.g. OZCF_Apples

registerHarvestSubmissionDetails(string,.details: Register a Harvest submission - it should add the Harvest submission to the array of Harvest submissions i.e. harvestMap.

params._growingCondtions: Claims related to growing conditions e.g. Organic vs Conventional i.e. harvest_description_json e.g. 'organic,pesticide free'
params._harvestDescription: Harvest specific comment e.g. Baby Marrows with soft skin and buttery flesh.
params._harvestID: Unique ID for supplier-produce and harvest combination e.g. 1b26557b-20f3-4ea2-81d2-e54c5a9a40f7
params._harvestQuantity: Quantity of harvested produce e.g. 10, includes  unit of measure e.g. bunches/KGs/none
params._harvestTableName: Table name for harvest entry in relational database e.g. foodprint_harvest
params._harvestUser: User who logged harvest e.g. useremail@xyz.com

registerStorageSubmission(string,string,.details: Register a Storage submission - it should add the Storage submission to the array of Storage submissions i.e. storageMap.

params._harvestID: Unique ID for harvest entry e.g. 1b26557b-20f3-4ea2-81d2-e54c5a9a40f7
params._otherID: Other IDs (e.g. supplier-produce and marketID) e.g. OZCF_Apples, OZCFM
params._storageDetail: Combination of storageDescription, storageTableName, storageUser and storageQuantity which includes storage UoM
params._storageID: Unique ID for storage entry e.g. 1b26557b-20f3-4ea2-81d2-e54c5a9a50be
params._storageTimeStamp: Date and time at which produce is harvested e.g. 20190620 16:10:55

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner.     * NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.
